{"tid":405203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【平衫的代價】一年見仔女2次 孟加拉女工時薪$2.5如現代奴隸","createTime":"2017-09-18T15:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T01:45:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fad482bbe34504d70ccf617e7df66a1a7acf140c","tid":405203,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170917/large/1505641565_d4e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170917%2Flarge%2F1505641565_d4e8.jpg&h=ecf67a92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現代的衣飾越賣越便宜，英國有些校服更只賣1.95鎊（19港元）兩件，但便宜背後，其實藏着一個個血汗工廠的悲慘故事。工廠工人人工微薄、工作時間長，工人之苦實不足為外人道。英國《每日郵報》記者揭露，孟加拉女工在悶熱的工廠內每天工作12小時，但時薪僅為25便士（2.6港元），由於家庭經濟能力有限，很多工人都無能力送子女上學，迫使孩子要早早輟學打工幫補家計。而工人為了賺錢養家，被迫與子女分開數百公里居住，每年只可探望子女兩次。<br />\n<br />\n這些血汗工廠為不少歐美著名大型連鎖集團生產衣服，例如Tesco、Asda、Aldi、Next等，工廠「NAZ」位於離首都達卡64公里的米爾扎布爾，專門生產Aldi馬球衫，工人月薪只有5,300孟加拉塔卡（470港元），另有500塔卡（44港元）準時上班獎金，但如果一個月有3天遲到逾5分鐘，獎金便會泡湯。<br />\n他們每周工作6天、48小時，但由於薪金微薄，不少工人都要加班增加收入，每天工作12小時，有時一周便達74小時，比孟加拉法定工時多出14小時。廠內女工獲悉她們製作的馬球衫，在英國的售價為兩件1.95鎊（19港元）、即比一杯咖啡便宜感到驚訝，「我希望購買這些廉價校服的英國家長，明白我們的工作有多艱苦，如果製造商可以稍為提高恤衫、裙子的售價，我們及孩子便可活得較好，我們生活很苦。」<br />\n達卡一間工廠的經理表示，想支付員工更多薪酬有心無力，因為零售商要將成本減至最低。《每日郵報》記者向Aldi查問，表示會立即全面調查。<br />\n另一間工廠「Ananta」專門為Next生產服裝，廠內30歲機器操作員納辛（Nashrin）表示，其14歲兒子Mannan最近輟學經營一個路邊茶檔，每天工作16小時，旨在增加家庭收入。「我感覺自己摧毁了兒子的未來，如果他們（工廠）給我更多人工，我當然會讓他繼續讀書，我希望他接受教育。」<br />\nNext發言人表示，自2010年起曾對工廠審核達10次，最近一次為今年4月，未有發現任何工資低於法定標準的情況。反對血汗工廠組織「Labour Behind The Label」的政策經理穆勒（Dominique Muller）批評，孟加拉的法定最低工資遠低於聯合國訂立的貧困線工資，只是工人們實際所需生活開支的三分一，簡直不可思議。「今年初孟加拉有工人抗議，要求增加最低工資，結果約3,500人被解僱，工會成員更被拘捕及起訴。」"},{"pid":"6ee7ece9dab68f03463b61229d6c7b9378f16139","tid":405203,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:00:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170918/57220931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170918%2F57220931&d=wca9uF3WYcW0QzuqSMqPTTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=915e4c33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170918%2F57220931&h=cd3d1a61\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170918/57220931</a>"},{"pid":"54df3ec68904b02e454b6ad338b4c790e070ecd1","tid":405203,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fc16e2c35aa54959aeb9f57b12a9a00fe4bede","tid":405203,"uid":84043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"我希望世界核平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ff37e5797f4307df154f6cc201b4e75354456d","tid":405203,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"孟加拉效應"},{"pid":"ccd4843b635ad15173e889ada780a34217cef89a","tid":405203,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:15:22.000Z","msg":"sosad"},{"pid":"d4d606bf83040616910716f8c50686896bea5606","tid":405203,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:19:59.000Z","msg":"你呀媽孟加拉你呀<br />\n<br />\n好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa177edb55ef722a0985276fc72e20f36eeae5a","tid":405203,"uid":109602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9652fec76eea0b4efafa41d2cc812f4b035c2386","tid":405203,"uid":109602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63b893a98b626743f8382f9ab95f1b69850271c3","tid":405203,"uid":119157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:28:26.000Z","msg":"齋講銀碼冇咩意思<br />\n<br />\n生活指數係點先？"},{"pid":"aae62e8cbc52d535e1c3da4db9357f3ea8bfb5b5","tid":405203,"uid":54264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:38:41.000Z","msg":"唔洗怕好快佢唔洗做 之前講美帝成衣自動化仲平過用血汗工廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff91c79899a9a1baab68ac2744fe915226773558","tid":405203,"uid":33756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"香港人每天工作十四小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3a60209f09b0c4e802364a278f205cd3f8383e","tid":405203,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗怕好快佢唔洗做 之前講美帝成衣自動化仲平過用血汗工廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實自然有其他出路<br />\n人總會有需求<br />\n總會有人出來想辦法滿足需求<br />\n只要唔好好似香港咁做咩都話犯法無牌<br />\n就一定有野做維持生存"},{"pid":"8884d115d1ea762d43e7a9cdfa1bd8de6b0cbf98","tid":405203,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:08:39.000Z","msg":"冇我買衫 佢屎都冇得食"},{"pid":"08fdb68eb116ec0ea1b67e953167811d572ddb93","tid":405203,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1150414fb17a9c204a24d2520e06fccc77c062fd","tid":405203,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:39:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇我買衫 佢屎都冇得食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沒有我們大陸人全球掃貨，你們腥港人早玩單了"},{"pid":"dc91baa866058798de4c32f37c4c14b6735e7164","tid":405203,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:53:11.000Z","msg":"其實你做廠都知，你估一年日日都咁長工時，春秋冬季個時，你數手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe560a0a38e36d35a9a23cb3109c13ac4303649b","tid":405203,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5907c739e6cd01fd3db30deffa0fe0992ae54959","tid":405203,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T21:29:30.000Z","msg":"人工看似好低，但對比起當地嘅住屋飲食係幾高先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n你英國人工高但d野貴呀嘛"},{"pid":"59ba8e975ac5b40a58855dc8bf54467605e12df7","tid":405203,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T21:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「我希望購買這些廉價校服的英國家長，明白我們的工作有多艱苦，如果製造商可以稍為提高恤衫、裙子的售價，我們及孩子便可活得較好，我們生活很苦。」</blockquote><br />\n唔好天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算賣貴啲<br />\n賺多咗嘅錢都唔會拎去做生產成本<br />\n生產成本從來都只會不停壓低<br />\n所以佢唔好諗住賣貴啲就可以提高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196273ee48b1b20711ecac482c0b924721e1d349","tid":405203,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T22:10:58.000Z","msg":"道德問題：回教國值唔值得可憐"},{"pid":"2d87e55a270fcbe90354990ba6a0f58af3c16b58","tid":405203,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T22:13:11.000Z","msg":"黎香港生活下，睇下邊個辛苦d"},{"pid":"31615e70fd4fad96a6b17784371162348a7eb231","tid":405203,"uid":42200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T23:22:50.000Z","msg":"跟本問題在於fast fashion, 個個brand 都想做h&amp;m"},{"pid":"0e798b72ac8cb077c9cd011c09d3304bf5ee8560","tid":405203,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T00:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣貴d有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，d客比既價一樣咁閪</blockquote><br />\n要出高d人工,成間廠搬埋去第2個國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d402f8ab12b9a21eefe5202f404f5cef7e7a1a7","tid":405203,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T00:34:44.000Z","msg":"如果唔係pr